Script Descriptions:

backup-esxi-host: Schedule daily esxi host backup and email the report.

iislog-archive: Move the IIS log that older than X days to the archive server.

hp-wireless-user: Add wirelss user in HP MSM720 AP.

mssql-db-restore: A example of restoring MSSQL from backup file.
